---
import Buttons from "./Buttons.astro";
---

<section class="nyhedsbrev">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Du kan beskytte naturen, dyrelivet og vores børn mod plastik</h1>
    <p>
      Kun med din støtte kan vi kæmpe for, at politikere og virksomheder tager
      ansvar for at standse overproduktion og forurening fra plastik nu og at vi
      kan uddanne fremtidens forbrugere.
    </p>
    <Buttons>Støt nu</Buttons>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  h1 {
    color: var(--color-complimentary-pine-green-dark, #142c2b);
    font-family: "Poppins";
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: normal;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-complimentary-pine-green-normal, #007c79);
    font-family: "Rubik";
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 150%;
    align-self: stretch;
  }
  .nyhedsbrev {
    display: flex;
    height: 34.25rem;
    padding: var(--spacing-section-padding-vertical, 5rem)
      var(--spacing-section-padding-horzontal, 8rem);
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .container {
    width: 46.375rem;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-text-gap-vertical, 2rem);
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  input[type="text"] {
    height: 3.125rem;
    min-width: 24.375rem;
    padding: 0.25rem var(--size-8, 0.5rem);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.625rem/;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    border: 0.5px solid #000;
    background: #f8f8f8;
  }

  input[type="submit"] {
    border-radius: 0.0625rem;
    background: var(--color-primary-cerise-red-normal, #e72458);
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    padding: var(--button-padding-vertical, 1rem)
      var(--button-padding-horizontal, 2rem);
  }

  input[type="submit"]::value {
    color: var(--color-secondary-white, #fff);
    text-align: center;
    font-family: Rubik;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 150.5%;
  }
</style>
